{"tid":1111493,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"支持心穎BB揮手區(抽水勿進)","createTime":"2019-04-17T02:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T11:41:42.000Z","uid":51814,"like":62,"dislike":1270,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"0394a19c5101ff3164b4775695ba97ef99a00cb9","tid":1111493,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"睇返心穎BB嘅星途其實都幾坎坷，由選港姐嗰時開始，做嘅角色永遠都係俾人恥笑，我覺得佢自己都心知，但係都仍然忍著淚水去逗觀眾開心。<br />\n<br />\n佢呢份真我嘅性格未必人人都接受到，在娛樂圈呢個咁虛偽嘅環境好難生存，漸漸亦都扭曲咗佢嘅人格。雖然佢表面上好強勢，事實佢嘅内心極需要人去愛同扶持，佢對身邊男性嘅苛索，係基於佢渴望追求者，可惜遇著毒撚馬明，佢永遠都要繼續做主動嗰個。<br />\n<br />\n佢今次一鋪清袋，應該好難再翻身，我唔想佢變到藍潔英咁樣，成為娛樂圈嘅犧牲品，大家俾次機會佢，令佢可以好似以前一樣搞笑，像一個開心BB，永遠做大家心目中嘅心穎BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/17/103905_c157013891fd303814c2671c60269bf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F17%2F103905_c157013891fd303814c2671c60269bf8.jpg&h=3538030b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e7da07b70358db8acd6d56416af8333083acdf2","tid":1111493,"uid":203417,"like":347,"dislike":2,"score":345,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"走啦"},{"pid":"cd6e61ff611fb21f80405e7d98c93515496c6c51","tid":1111493,"uid":195444,"like":373,"dislike":4,"score":369,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"我支持屌樓主老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d2864ce3a35b591170bf81fad9b25790e1a146","tid":1111493,"uid":50428,"like":265,"dislike":4,"score":261,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"支持佢仆街翻唔到身。<br />\n呢啲閪女人靠個閪都搵食，被踢爆生活都好過大部份人啦。"},{"pid":"8f27ee11e57d8cd3c0eab5d27d49feb1c751aad8","tid":1111493,"uid":51814,"like":2,"dislike":156,"score":-154,"quote":{"pid":"2e7da07b70358db8acd6d56416af8333083acdf2","tid":1111493,"uid":203417,"like":347,"dislike":2,"score":345,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"走啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:47: