去愛同扶持，佢對身邊男性嘅苛索，係基於佢渴望追求者，可惜遇著毒撚馬明，佢永遠都要繼續做主動嗰個。<br />\n<br />\n佢今次一鋪清袋，應該好難再翻身，我唔想佢變到藍潔英咁樣，成為娛樂圈嘅犧牲品，大家俾次機會佢，令佢可以好似以前一樣搞笑，像一個開心BB，永遠做大家心目中嘅心穎BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/17/103905_c157013891fd303814c2671c60269bf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F17%2F103905_c157013891fd303814c2671c60269bf8.jpg&h=3538030b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"On9樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41d2d59c69549db163e55ae0f680dec88229037","tid":1111493,"uid":227032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:06:21.000Z","msg":"BB前，BB後 好撚核突呀<br />\n人地改左名叫心穎GG囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21640db9118a6c80eb5919ed6c7d29c0ba9d18db","tid":1111493,"uid":138661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"adb59d316be02a45f8da5dd4894067a068bf46c6","tid":1111493,"uid":51814,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"7e7b73d82d3d9f90294e353f8f65e62fd6d952d6","tid":1111493,"uid":138661,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:28:50.000Z","msg":"佢有男朋友派綠帽<br />\n乘機同sammi做friend 仲食埋人老公<br />\n咁都要支持？<br />\n心機婊嚟喎 ching"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"事實係咪咁冇人知，心穎BB鬼妹仔性格，遇上心儀偶像，用身體接觸表示好鐘意佢都好正常，加上飲酒亂性就更加令淫底原形畢露，以前sammi都成日同華仔攬埋一舊，只係華仔唔蘇佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:08:01.000Z","msg":"唔好合理化鬼妹仔性格就可以酒後想點就點啦<br />\n仲話好正常<br />\n你條女色心起同第條仔扑野 係咪可以話佢咁係人既本性而接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6663e67abe411fbf300540d1e2464bfc1528e3","tid":1111493,"uid":243856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:1